title: Rare T206 find- Nap Lajoie/American Beauty back

posts.post_title: Rare T206 find- Nap Lajoie/American Beauty back
posts.post_content: I looked at a nice collection of T206s a few days ago. The owner wasn’t ready to part with most of them but I was able snag this card- T206 Lajoie with an American Beauty back. Pop 5, now pop 6! Looking to trade for a low grade 1914 Cracker Jack Cobb
